      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "FASCINATE GLORY (8) jumped from out wide and was game in defeat last start when a 0.8 lengths third (16.20) behind ROLLED YOU at this track. Although beaten ran one of the quickest times on the card last start. Well-placed to take this out. LADY LUELLA (1) has been hard to follow lately, running seventh (19.06) last time but prior to that ran very well when placed at Richmond. Can improve sharply here. REBEL FORCE (2) is worth forgiving last start after finishing fourth (16.38) from Box 5 at this track over 272m. Comes through a solid form race last start. Should be in this for a long way. WOW PARTY TIME (5) missed the placings here most recently but can sneak into the finish with the right run.",
